New Year Celebration organised by the Sultan of Brunei.
Live performance on 31-12-1996 as part of the HIStory World Tour.
The show on this release was organised by the Royal Family of Brunei. The background story of this release is uncertain. It is believed that the Royal Family produced these releases for invited guests.
The show was recorded and produced by Sensible Music Group, based in the UK (https://www.sensible-music.co.uk/). Some sources claim the copyrights to this show were part of the contract between the popstar and the Royal Family, however this is not confirmed.
These items were not released to the public and are not released on the Sony and MJJ Music labels.
